    <name>SimpliPlay</name>
    <summary>Simple FOSS media player</summary>
    <developer id="me.anirudhsevugan.SimpliPlay">
        <name>Anirudh S</name>
    </developer>
    <content_rating type="oars-1.1" />
    <branding>
        <color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#1a73e8</color>
        <color type="primary" scheme_preference="dark">#083358</color>
    </branding>
    <description>
    <p>SimpliPlay is a simple media player that's free forever and supports various multimedia formats such as HLS and MPEG-DASH, plus support for customization via add-ons.</p>

    <p>SimpliPlay lets you play media with features such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Play from HLS and MPEG-DASH streams, as well as files using H.264, VP9, AV1, and more</li>
        <li>Use add-ons coded in JavaScript to customize media playback, from custom skins to new features</li>
        <li>WebVTT and SRT subtitles support</li>
        <li>Take snapshots with Ctrl+S to capture perfect moments in your media, as well as any add-ons you've created</li>
        <li>Use DevTools (identical to what's in Chrome) to edit code for the player in realtime</li>
    </ul>
    </description>
